# RingCentral API reference (this repo)

## Skills (full docs)

- Claude/Cursor skill: `.claude/skills/ringcentral-api/SKILL.md` — RingCentral REST API, SDKs, Embeddable voice widget, WebRTC, SMS, and auth.

- Official: [RingCentral Developers](https://developers.ringcentral.com/) · [API Reference](https://developers.ringcentral.com/api-reference) · [RingCentral Embeddable](https://github.com/ringcentral/ringcentral-embeddable)

## Auth wiring

- Prefer using the official RingCentral SDK (`@ringcentral/sdk` for Node.js) for authentication.
- Auth Flow: JWT is recommended for server-to-server integrations. Authorization Code with PKCE is for user-facing applications.
- Production base URL: `https://platform.ringcentral.com`

## RingCentral Embeddable Widget

- Injected via a `<script>` tag referencing `adapter.js`.
- Interacts with the parent application using `window.postMessage` (e.g., `rc-call-ring-notify`, `rc-adapter-new-call`).
- Uses WebRTC, requiring the application to be served over HTTPS.
- **OAuth Redirect URI** (Developer Console → Auth) must be exactly:
  `https://apps.ringcentral.com/integration/ringcentral-embeddable/latest/redirect.html`
  — **not** your Render URL. Empty redirect list → `invalid_client` / OAU-113.
